February isn’t just Black History Month but also a month of love and appreciation for your loved ones, and for those in a relationship, it’s time to start thinking of how you would like to celebrate that love. There are a vast number of songs that will help express your passion and love.  While you are thinking of songs to put into a Valentine’s Day playlist, make sure to think of moments from your relationship that a song you may relate to think about your partner and their personality and think of things you would like to say that you may have a difficult time communicating. If Wondering what to listen to this month, with Valentine’s Day right around the corner here is in no particular order, our 10 Favorite Love songs you must add to your February playlist. Perfect music for this love season          